en_773066_0	6 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) troops of the 572 Brigade under the 57 Division of the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) considering the humanitarian aspect, put up a temporary house for a physically-handicapped man and his family in the general area of Thottadi.
en_773066_1	On being informed of his helpless predicament due to absence of a shelter, troops kept the Commanding Officer, 6 SLSR informed of the plight of this innocent civilian and his family with children.
en_773066_2	Accordingly, the Commanding Officer and troops after meeting the disabled person agreed to put up a temporary shelter with the raw materials available with the Army as an immediate relief measure.
